social_posts.post_text:
Móyòsóré Martins’s works are arresting on sight, and made more so by an understanding of the symbols scattered throughout the paintings. As Moyo grew up surrounded by different forms and understandings of religion, this piece speaks to the contrasts of religion and spirituality. See this piece in person at @artmiamifairs, Booth AM526. 

#artmiami #moyosoremartins #blueinterior #miamiartscene #abstractpainting #figurativepainting #moyo
